    • Method Detail

      • ButtonLayout

        static void ButtonLayout(int Base)
        This functions is used to alter the buttons of the calculator based on the current base the calculator is set on. Depending on the Base that is passed in the parameter, the buttons are enabled or disabled. The buttons are disabled or enabled using 'setEnabled' and a simply expressions that will be true or false (i.e. Base >= 11, for Base 10). Each button will be checked.
        Parameters:
        Base - Is an int that represents the number base.
